    <p><span style="font-size:26px;"><span style="color:#000000;">Albany R-III Related: Coronavirus (COVID-19) Information Page</span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;"> </p>

<p> </p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong><span style="font-size:22px;"><a href="/vimages/shared/vnews/stories/5e6ff20f240cd/March-31-2020%20-%20AlbanyR3-Parent-Letter.pdf" target="_blank" title="SPECIAL LETTER to Parents from ALBANY R-III ADMINISTRATION"><span style="color:#e74c3c;">SPECIAL LETTER to Parents from ALBANY R-III ADMINISTRATION</span></a></span></strong></p>

<p> </p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong><span style="color:#c0392b;"><span style="font-size:18px;">School will be closed through April 28, 2020.</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong><span style="color:#c0392b;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><u>Zoom</u> is currently Disabled for All Students.  Please use Google Hangouts.</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong><span style="color:#c0392b;"><span style="font-size:18px;">Adventure Club / Wee Care will be closed March 18, 2020 - April 28, 2020.</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><strong><span style="color:#c0392b;"><span style="font-size:18px;">No Practices or any other activities during this time.</span></span></strong></p>

<p><span style="color:#c0392b;"><span style="font-size:18px;"> </span></span></p>

<ul style="margin-left: 80px;">
<li>
